  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the air fryer to 375°F (190°C).",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together the egg, Greek yogurt, lemon juice, and lemon zest.",
    "Add the minced garlic, chopped parsley, crumbled feta cheese, pitted olives, canned artichoke hearts, and grated Vialone-Nano rice to the bowl.",
    "Mix well to combine, until the ingredients are evenly distributed.",
    "Using a 1/4 cup measuring cup, scoop the mixture into the air fryer basket.",
    "Spray the tops of the fritters with cooking spray to prevent sticking.",
    "Cook the fritters in the air fryer for 8-10 minutes, or until golden brown and crispy.",
    "Remove the fritters from the air fryer and serve hot."
